      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2000351-the-house-on-mango-street">Quotes from The House on Mang...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
